r就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共見到就自然對放自由行落黎有所顧慮，將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LK1AcwV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLK1AcwV.png&h=bc3aa378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Inb3LozLechFax4NQN-nC01aVeLJE2Mv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1Inb3LozLechFax4NQN-nC01aVeLJE2Mv&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Xs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=92d7691b\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Inb3LozLechFax4NQN-nC01aVeLJE2Mv</a>"},{"pid":"61366ed00bde1a2b5247fc3d67ac5cd50be685ac","tid":1469811,"uid":190285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3ed5875a6c673b83cc66c06350989db48fb5b17","tid":1469811,"uid":243871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"捉到811兇手"}]}